      Parses a String representation of a DbSet into a DbSet.
      Type Parameters:
      E - The type of the elements in this set.
      Parameters:

      s - The String to parse.
      elementToString - The function used to convert an element of this set into a String. Used when creating a new set.
      elementFromString - The function used to convert an element of this set into a String. Used when creating a new set.
      Returns:
